Hello Guys,

I made a new Map called bhop_simpletrees.
Like it says in the name i tried to keep it as simple as possible.
If you find some bugs you can always report the bug in the comment section.

      About the map:

  • This map has one big stage.
  • Difficulty is Tier 1
  • You could run this map in under 15 seconds.
  • I made this map in 2 days.
  • You can do the bonus wherever you want.
If you want you can send me your runs of this map and i'll put it in the desc.

My Run



Have fun playing it!
